11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_UTILITY_CASCADED_BIQUAD_FILTER_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_UTILITY_CASCADED_BIQUAD_FILTER_H_
13
14#include <stddef.h>
15
16#include <complex>
17#include <vector>
18
19#include "api/array_view.h"
20
21namespace webrtc {
22
23// Applies a number of biquads in a cascaded manner. The filter implementation
24// is direct form 1.
25class CascadedBiQuadFilter {
26 public:
27 struct BiQuadParam {
28 BiQuadParam(std::complex<float> zero,
29 std::complex<float> pole,
30 float gain,
31 bool mirror_zero_along_i_axis = false);
32 explicit BiQuadParam(const BiQuadParam&);
33 std::complex<float> zero;
34 std::complex<float> pole;
35 float gain;
36 bool mirror_zero_along_i_axis;
37 };
38
39 struct BiQuadCoefficients {
40 float b[3];
41 float a[2];
42 };
43
44 struct BiQuad {
45 explicit BiQuad(const BiQuadCoefficients& coefficients)
46 : coefficients(coefficients), x(), y() {}
47 explicit BiQuad(const CascadedBiQuadFilter::BiQuadParam& param);
48 void Reset();
49 BiQuadCoefficients coefficients;
50 float x[2];
51 float y[2];
52 };
53
54 CascadedBiQuadFilter(
55 const CascadedBiQuadFilter::BiQuadCoefficients& coefficients,
56 size_t num_biquads);
57 explicit CascadedBiQuadFilter(
58 const std::vector<CascadedBiQuadFilter::BiQuadParam>& biquad_params);
59 ~CascadedBiQuadFilter();
60 CascadedBiQuadFilter(const CascadedBiQuadFilter&) = delete;
61 CascadedBiQuadFilter& operator=(const CascadedBiQuadFilter&) = delete;
62
63 // Applies the biquads on the values in x in order to form the output in y.
64 void Process(rtc::ArrayView<const float> x, rtc::ArrayView<float> y);
65 // Applies the biquads on the values in y in an in-place manner.
66 void Process(rtc::ArrayView<float> y);
67 // Resets the filter to its initial state.
68 void Reset();
69
70 private:
71 void ApplyBiQuad(rtc::ArrayView<const float> x,
72 rtc::ArrayView<float> y,
73 CascadedBiQuadFilter::BiQuad* biquad);
74
75 std::vector<BiQuad> biquads_;
76};
77
78} // namespace webrtc
79
80#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_UTILITY_CASCADED_BIQUAD_FILTER_H_
